# 安裝指南 (CUDA 12.2)

請**按順序**執行以下安裝步驟。

---

## 步驟 1: 建立 Conda 環境

```bash
conda create -n bge-reranker python=3.10 -y
conda activate bge-reranker
```

---

## 步驟 2: 安裝 PyTorch (CUDA 12.1 相容 12.2)

```bash
pip install torch==2.2.0 torchvision==0.17.0 torchaudio==2.2.0 --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu121
```

> 註：PyTorch cu121 版本可以在 CUDA 12.2 上運行

**驗證安裝：**
```bash
python -c "import torch; print(f'PyTorch: {torch.__version__}'); print(f'CUDA available: {torch.cuda.is_available()}'); print(f'CUDA version: {torch.version.cuda}')"
```

---

## 步驟 3: 安裝 Transformers 相關

```bash
pip install transformers==4.40.0
pip install datasets==2.19.0
pip install accelerate==0.29.0
pip install tokenizers==0.19.0
```

---

## 步驟 4: 安裝 DeepSpeed

```bash
pip install deepspeed==0.14.0
```

**驗證：**
```bash
ds_report
```

---

## 步驟 5: 安裝 FlagEmbedding

```bash
pip install FlagEmbedding==1.2.10
```

若要使用 finetune 功能：
```bash
pip install "FlagEmbedding[finetune]"
```

---

## 步驟 6: 安裝其他依賴

```bash
pip install tqdm
pip install tensorboard
pip install huggingface_hub
pip install peft  # 若需要 LoRA
```

---

## 完整安裝指令 (一鍵)

如果你想一次安裝所有套件：

```bash
# 建立環境
conda create -n bge-reranker python=3.10 -y
conda activate bge-reranker

# PyTorch (CUDA 12.1/12.2)
pip install torch==2.2.0 torchvision==0.17.0 torchaudio==2.2.0 --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu121

# Transformers 生態系
pip install transformers==4.40.0 datasets==2.19.0 accelerate==0.29.0 tokenizers==0.19.0

# DeepSpeed
pip install deepspeed==0.14.0

# FlagEmbedding
pip install "FlagEmbedding[finetune]"

# 其他
pip install tqdm tensorboard huggingface_hub peft
```

---

## 驗證安裝

執行以下 Python 腳本確認所有套件正確安裝：

```python
import torch
import transformers
import datasets
import accelerate
import deepspeed
import FlagEmbedding

print(f"PyTorch: {torch.__version__}")
print(f"CUDA available: {torch.cuda.is_available()}")
print(f"CUDA version: {torch.version.cuda}")
print(f"Transformers: {transformers.__version__}")
print(f"Datasets: {datasets.__version__}")
print(f"Accelerate: {accelerate.__version__}")
print(f"DeepSpeed: {deepspeed.__version__}")
print(f"FlagEmbedding: {FlagEmbedding.__version__}")
print("\n✓ 所有套件安裝成功！")
```

